{
  "stem": "13817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were a little careful-- my brother, and my mother, and myself-- because we wanted to get the feel of the place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, we-- we just scouted around what-- what was going on and how we could find the other place to live instead of with 30 people in one room, and-- which-- which my-- my brother and my mother did after a little while.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After I was gone, I found out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the beginning, when I was in Posen, I could receive pre-printed cards from my-- from-- from the ghetto into-- into the camp, just for a few months.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then that all broke down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there, again, there were some hints what was going on when I noticed the change of address and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I-- I got a hint what-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they were establishing some kind of a living condition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, I was-- when we-- when the train arrived, we were with 280, like I said, European for-- of this newcomers into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we were in Posen-- or this Poznanski, I think, in Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- where we were put into a-- to a camp, which was-- which used to be a factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one room of that factory was emptied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were along the walls were two tiers of bombs-- continuous tiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the middle was a big bellies-- belly button stove-- or how do you call them-- them briquette ovens to heat the place?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were told we had to-- we would go out with the other people who were already that camp for months and months and circled with-- with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was not-- it was not under the SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The guards were not SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
